description:
Subjects Addressed: (1) “Behold, I come as a thief. Blessed is he that watcheth, and keepeth his garments, lest he walk naked, and they see his shame." Revelation 16:15.
(2) The judgment is now passing in the sanctuary above. Soon--none know how soon--it will pass to the cases of the living. "If therefore thou shalt not watch, I will come on thee as a thief, and thou shalt not know what hour I will come upon thee." Revelation 3:3. (12:46)
(3) As the goodman needs to be watchful to know when the thief is coming in order to be prepared, so God’s people should know the time period when “Jesus comes as a thief.” (17:38)
(4) Joe Biden and Pope Francis team up. Pope Francis calls for universal access to health care. (29:48)
(5) For all the major problems facing the world, Pope Francis is calling for the union of all nations and churches. (31:21)
(6) Joe Biden and Pope Francis team up to bring about universal health care, but God’s people cannot support nor unite with them. The temperance movement is connected with the Sunday Law. (35:11)
(7) Madeleine Albright and John Kerry call for a union of church of state to combat global crises. (36:14)
(8) Earth Day is connected to the Sunday Law movement. (38:16)
(9) Pope Francis states that personal religion must be laid aside, everyone must unite, to save the earth. (39:42)
(10) The Sunday movement is now making its way in darkness. The leaders are concealing the true issue…Its professions are mild and apparently Christian, but when it shall speak it will reveal the spirit of the dragon…We should bring before them the real question at issue, thus interposing the most effectual protest against measures to restrict liberty of conscience. (41:07)
(11) We know that Jesus is about to come as a thief when the SDA church leaders and people are crying “peace and safety.” (44:48) 
(12) What is the work of preparation to meet Jesus when He comes as a thief? (1:04:07)
